/target
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb
Cargo.lock.orig
.DS_Store

# Cargo.lock IS committed here (not the usual lib convention): the MSRV-1.82
# build needs the exact transitive pins that dodge edition-2024/rustc-1.85
# dependencies (idna_adapter, zeroize, hyper-rustls, rustls, ...). CI resolves
# against this lock so the matrix stays reproducible.
